
<p>Reuters <strong><a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-asks-banks-limit-some-connect-bond-outflows-sources-2023-08-25/">exclusively reported</a></strong> that China’s central bank has asked domestic banks to limit outflows into foreign bonds, the latest in the raft of steps authorities are taking to contain yuan weakness. </p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.reutersagency.com/en/reutersbest/article/china-steps-up-yuan-defence-with-bond-limit-guidance/">China steps up yuan defence with bond limit guidance </a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.reutersagency.com/en/">Reuters News Agency</a>.</p>
